column1: Pumping Station found marked on 1946 OS map
Altitude changed from 5ft to 10ft and one pencil mark says 20ft – actually about 15ft
1960 Jan 22nd Inspection recommended moving gauges 10yrds WNW to reduce over shelter
No note as to whether or when this happened, but the altitude for 1960 changed from 5ft to 10ft
Notes in red say values were corrected 12.1.60, but not why, or where the new values came from
